  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/bc5b653b421af728282836fae11b433c.avif?t=1745337196\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras_big/bc5b653b421af728282836fae11b433c.avif?t=1745337196 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ratico Puzzle Adventure transforms into an engaging casual puzzle game that offers players a delightful and brain-teasing experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/a9005e47944940fb3f820dabe8e0308a.poster.avif?t=1745337196\" width=300 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/a9005e47944940fb3f820dabe8e0308a.webm?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/a9005e47944940fb3f820dabe8e0308a.mp4?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With its charming minimalist design and an emphasis on relaxed gameplay, this game is perfect for those seeking a more leisurely gaming experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/f8df3c753c7807e7f8078240780abaaf.poster.avif?t=1745337196\" width=300 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/f8df3c753c7807e7f8078240780abaaf.webm?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/f8df3c753c7807e7f8078240780abaaf.mp4?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of a clever rat with unique abilities, ready to tackle various puzzling challenges and obstacles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/229bbe1e11c909f31d33186cdaaa09f6.poster.avif?t=1745337196\" width=300 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/229bbe1e11c909f31d33186cdaaa09f6.webm?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/229bbe1e11c909f31d33186cdaaa09f6.mp4?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're navigating intricate mazes or utilizing your wit to overcome hazards, your goal remains the same: guide the resourceful rodent to the cherished cheese in each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/422416aa021afd036264dcc0318e21f2.poster.avif?t=1745337196\" width=300 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/422416aa021afd036264dcc0318e21f2.webm?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/422416aa021afd036264dcc0318e21f2.mp4?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80 Puzzling Levels: \"Ratico Puzzle Adventure\" presents a rich collection of levels that promise hours of enjoyable gameplay, with puzzle complexity increasing as you progress. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No Pressure, No Limits: Unlike traditional games, \"Ratico Puzzle Adventure\" allows unlimited attempts to conquer each puzzle, promoting a relaxed and stress-free gaming atmosphere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >User-Friendly Controls: The controls are intuitively designed to ensure a seamless experience, making it accessible to players of all skill levels. While a gamepad is recommended, you can enjoy the game with ease using various input devices.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/bc5b653b421af728282836fae11b433c.avif?t=1745337196\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras_big/bc5b653b421af728282836fae11b433c.avif?t=1745337196 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ratico Puzzle Adventure transforms into an engaging casual puzzle game that offers players a delightful and brain-teasing experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/a9005e47944940fb3f820dabe8e0308a.poster.avif?t=1745337196\" width=300 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/a9005e47944940fb3f820dabe8e0308a.webm?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/a9005e47944940fb3f820dabe8e0308a.mp4?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With its charming minimalist design and an emphasis on relaxed gameplay, this game is perfect for those seeking a more leisurely gaming experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/f8df3c753c7807e7f8078240780abaaf.poster.avif?t=1745337196\" width=300 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/f8df3c753c7807e7f8078240780abaaf.webm?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/f8df3c753c7807e7f8078240780abaaf.mp4?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of a clever rat with unique abilities, ready to tackle various puzzling challenges and obstacles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/229bbe1e11c909f31d33186cdaaa09f6.poster.avif?t=1745337196\" width=300 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/229bbe1e11c909f31d33186cdaaa09f6.webm?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/229bbe1e11c909f31d33186cdaaa09f6.mp4?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're navigating intricate mazes or utilizing your wit to overcome hazards, your goal remains the same: guide the resourceful rodent to the cherished cheese in each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/422416aa021afd036264dcc0318e21f2.poster.avif?t=1745337196\" width=300 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/422416aa021afd036264dcc0318e21f2.webm?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312480/extras/422416aa021afd036264dcc0318e21f2.mp4?t=1745337196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80 Puzzling Levels: \"Ratico Puzzle Adventure\" presents a rich collection of levels that promise hours of enjoyable gameplay, with puzzle complexity increasing as you progress. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No Pressure, No Limits: Unlike traditional games, \"Ratico Puzzle Adventure\" allows unlimited attempts to conquer each puzzle, promoting a relaxed and stress-free gaming atmosphere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >User-Friendly Controls: The controls are intuitively designed to ensure a seamless experience, making it accessible to players of all skill levels. While a gamepad is recommended, you can enjoy the game with ease using various input devices.</p></li></ul>",
